Zero tacche sullo smartphone? La classifica 2026 degli operatori che prendono ovunque

Di Francesca Testa

25 Gen 2026

<img 
                                        fetchpriority="high" 
                                        width="741" 
                                        height="486" 
                                        class="entry-thumb" 
                                        src="https://www.macitynet.it/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/Segnale-Cellulare-24-1-2026-www-Macitynet-it-741x486.jpg" srcset="https://www.macitynet.it/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/Segnale-Cellulare-24-1-2026-www-Macitynet-it-741x486.jpg 741w, https://www.macitynet.it/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/Segnale-Cellulare-24-1-2026-www-Macitynet-it-50x33.jpg 50w, https://www.macitynet.it/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/Segnale-Cellulare-24-1-2026-www-Macitynet-it-75x50.jpg 75w, https://www.macitynet.it/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/Segnale-Cellulare-24-1-2026-www-Macitynet-it-100x67.jpg 100w" sizes="(max-width: 741px) 100vw, 741px" 
